com.tractrac.model.lib.api.data

Interface IMessageData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITimeData

    public interface IMessageData
extends ITimeData

    A generic message object that can transfer messages either as text or as binary large object (blob).

    The type of message is defined by the kind integer returned by getKind. All messages of the same kind will have the same kind id number.

    The message is usually either text or blob, and one of them will usually return null. It is up to the user to know the kind of data and process it accordingly

    Author:
    Jesper Grooss
